00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:03.950 align:middle line:10%
of how that occurs.

00:07:03.950 --> 00:07:07.310 align:middle line:84%
>> The answers may lie in the
fundamental shift which is

00:07:07.310 --> 00:07:10.730 align:middle line:84%
occurring in our
understanding of our universe.

00:07:10.730 --> 00:07:13.610 align:middle line:10%
>> Virtually every ancient
culture and every native

00:07:13.610 --> 00:07:17.540 align:middle line:10%
culture has thought of
the universe as a unity,

00:07:17.540 --> 00:07:21.350 align:middle line:10%
as a circle, and man as
being central to that.

00:07:21.350 --> 00:07:22.850 align:middle line:84%
And it was only
with the discoveries

00:07:22.850 --> 00:07:26.090 align:middle line:84%
of Isaac Newton
