00:07:35.510 --> 00:07:37.550 align:middle line:90%
are separate from each other.

00:07:37.550 --> 00:07:40.280 align:middle line:84%
And that idea of separation
is the foundation

00:07:40.280 --> 00:07:41.185 align:middle line:90%
of Western thinking.

00:07:41.185 --> 00:07:44.340 align:middle line:90%


00:07:44.340 --> 00:07:49.020 align:middle line:84%
Now Newton described a
very well-behaved universe

00:07:49.020 --> 00:07:52.710 align:middle line:84%
of separate things
operating in space and time,

00:07:52.710 --> 00:07:56.520 align:middle line:90%
according to fixed laws.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:59.130 align:middle line:10%
The idea of the body
as machine, the body

00:07:59.130 --> 00:08:02.640 align:middle line:10%
as this well-behaved
machine with the two

00:08:02.640 --> 00:08:05.580 align:middle line:10%
engines of the body being
the brain and the heart,

00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:11.490 align:middle line:10%
and the whole central orchestra
being conducted by DNA.

00:08:11.490 --> 00:08:13.110 align:middle line:90%
That's the model we have.

00:08:13.110 --> 00:08:15.840 align:middle line:84%
And we think of
various processes

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:19.350 align:middle line:84%
being localized in
certain parts of the body.

00:08:19.350 --> 00:08:22.620 align:middle line:84%
What's wrong with that
is just about everything.

00:08:22.620 --> 00:08:25.530 align:middle line:84%
Body is completely
decentralized.

00:08:25.530 --> 00:08:29.390 align:middle line:84%
There is no central
brain, in a sense.

00:08:29.390 --> 00:08:33.470 align:middle line:84%
And that the brain is closer
to an antenna receiver.

00:08:33.470 --> 00:08:37.020 align:middle line:84%
It's closer to a transducer
of information, a receiver

00:08:37.020 --> 00:08:38.789 align:middle line:84%
and a transmitter
of information,

00:08:38.789 --> 00:08:42.710 align:middle line:84%
but not the central repository
of that information.

00:08:42.710 --> 00:08:45.570 align:middle line:10%
>> In our conventional world
of biochemistry and cellular

00:08:45.570 --> 00:08:49.440 align:middle line:10%
biology, we focus on a Newtonian
belief of a material world.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.210 align:middle line:84%
Through the history
of science, we've

00:08:51.210 --> 00:08:53.440 align:middle line:84%
focused on the
mechanical reality,

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:57.030 align:middle line:84%
and have let go of the
concept of energy and fields

00:08:57.030 --> 00:08:58.980 align:middle line:90%
as information in biology.

00:08:58.980 --> 00:09:02.400 align:middle line:84%
That's the Newtonian perspective
that says, focus on the matter.

00:09:02.400 --> 00:09:04.920 align:middle line:84%
Don't pay attention to
the rest of the stuff.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.590 align:middle line:84%
Except that we're
now recognizing

00:09:06.590 --> 00:09:10.440 align:middle line:84%
that the mind, which is an
energetic field of thought,

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:13.800 align:middle line:84%
which you can read with
EEG wires on your brain,

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:16.920 align:middle line:84%
or even more interesting
is a new process called

00:09:16.920 --> 00:09:20.070 align:middle line:84%
magnetoencephalograph,
called MEG--

00:09:20.070 --> 00:09:22.890 align:middle line:84%
well, electroencephalograph,
you put wires on the skin

00:09:22.890 --> 00:09:25.950 align:middle line:84%
and read brain activity,
magnetoencephalograph

00:09:25.950 --> 00:09:29.160 align:middle line:90%
is a probe outside of the head.

00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:32.490 align:middle line:84%
And it reads the fields
of neural activity

00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:34.279 align:middle line:90%
without even touching the body.

00:09:34.279 --> 00:09:35.820 align:middle line:84%
So it basically says
that when you're

00:09:35.820 --> 00:09:39.430 align:middle line:84%
processing with your brain,
you're broadcasting fields.

00:09:39.430 --> 00:09:43.290 align:middle line:84%
>> 1875 to 1920 was
this enormous growth

00:09:43.290 --> 00:09:45.330 align:middle line:90%
of biochemistry.

00:09:45.330 --> 00:09:47.910 align:middle line:10%
And it was then thought that
chemistry is probably--you

00:09:47.910 --> 00:09:48.710 align:middle line:10%
know--

00:09:48.710 --> 00:09:50.080 align:middle line:10%
we're a chemical machine.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.590 align:middle line:10%
The answer is to put the
right chemical in the body,

00:09:52.590 --> 00:09:53.820 align:middle line:10%
and you'll get better.

00:09:53.820 --> 00:09:55.860 align:middle line:90%
To a point, that's correct.

00:09:55.860 --> 00:09:59.730 align:middle line:84%
But it doesn't appear to be
correct for chronic disease.

00:09:59.730 --> 00:10:02.990 align:middle line:90%
It's correct in the short term.

00:10:02.990 --> 00:10:07.090 align:middle line:84%
There was a major
intellectual split going on

00:10:07.090 --> 00:10:10.450 align:middle line:84%
at the time in physics,
because the old Newtonian

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:15.790 align:middle line:84%
world, the clockwork
universe, was going strong.

00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:18.280 align:middle line:84%
And a few crackpots
in Denmark, Germany,

00:10:18.280 --> 00:10:21.760 align:middle line:84%
and to a lesser extent, England,
developed quantum physics

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:25.810 align:middle line:84%
and said that it doesn't work
the way you said it works.

00:10:25.810 --> 00:10:28.190 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't happen like that.

00:10:28.190 --> 00:10:31.420 align:middle line:84%
And there were huge
anomalies found in physics

00:10:31.420 --> 00:10:33.640 align:middle line:90%
that could not be explained.

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:36.280 align:middle line:84%
And the upshot of this
was that the old idea

00:10:36.280 --> 00:10:39.040 align:middle line:84%
of a mechanical universe,
where everything

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:43.380 align:middle line:84%
happens for a specific reason in
its own way, had to be dropped.

00:10:43.380 --> 00:10:46.370 align:middle line:90%


00:10:46.370 --> 00:10:49.640 align:middle line:84%
>> Quantum physics changed our
perception of reality over 80

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:50.780 align:middle line:90%
years ago.

00:10:50.780 --> 00:10:53.630 align:middle line:84%
Surprisingly, this
new viewpoint has yet

00:10:53.630 --> 00:10:57.110 align:middle line:84%
to be incorporated into
our current biology model.

00:10:57.110 --> 00:10:59.510 align:middle line:10%
>> The main problem with the
current biological model is

00:10:59.510 --> 00:11:02.280 align:middle line:10%
that it's reductionist
and mechanistic.

00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:05.360 align:middle line:10%
That means first, it tries
to explain everything

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:07.879 align:middle line:10%
in terms of little bits.

00:11:07.879 --> 00:11:09.420 align:middle line:84%
Generally, molecules,
because they're

00:11:09.420 --> 00:11:12.680 align:middle line:84%
the smallest things
in organisms.

00:11:12.680 --> 00:11:15.830 align:middle line:84%
And secondly, it tries
to treat the organism

00:11:15.830 --> 00:11:17.960 align:middle line:84%
as a machine that
works simply in terms

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:20.120 align:middle line:90%
of physics and chemistry.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:23.570 align:middle line:10%
>> Chemical reaction in the
body is supposed to be central,

00:11:23.570 --> 00:11:27.800 align:middle line:10%
and the main reason it occurs,
according to current theory,

00:11:27.800 --> 00:11:30.650 align:middle line:10%
is through molecular collision.

00:11:30.650 --> 00:11:33.410 align:middle line:84%
So that one molecule
collides into another,

00:11:33.410 --> 00:11:36.740 align:middle line:84%
and that's how they
have this information,

00:11:36.740 --> 00:11:40.890 align:middle line:84%
and how we have a cascade
of chemical processes.

00:11:40.890 --> 00:11:43.640 align:middle line:84%
Now if you think
of the usual cell,

00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:46.070 align:middle line:84%
a cell is like a swimming
pool, and molecules

00:11:46.070 --> 00:11:49.190 align:middle line:84%
are like a couple of tennis
balls in that swimming pool.

00:11:49.190 --> 00:11:51.794 align:middle line:84%
And according to this
theory, one tennis ball

00:11:51.794 --> 00:11:53.210 align:middle line:84%
is supposed to
find another tennis

00:11:53.210 --> 00:11:58.710 align:middle line:84%
ball in this vast body of water,
and do so instantaneously.

00:11:58.710 --> 00:12:02.090 align:middle line:84%
