00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:55.760 align:middle line:84%
It had to do with
subtle energies.

00:16:55.760 --> 00:16:57.950 align:middle line:84%
And we took them through
this training program,

00:16:57.950 --> 00:17:00.290 align:middle line:84%
