00:17:26.510 --> 00:17:28.280 align:middle line:90%
Breathe deeply now.

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:30.290 align:middle line:84%
We could rule out
any of those kind

00:17:30.290 --> 00:17:33.680 align:middle line:90%
