00:17:42.530 --> 00:17:43.790 align:middle line:90%
screen.

00:17:43.790 --> 00:17:46.550 align:middle line:84%
And then at random times
throughout the session,

00:17:46.550 --> 00:17:50.360 align:middle line:84%
they were asked to send
loving, compassionate intention

00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:52.070 align:middle line:90%
