activity of this person

00:18:07.250 --> 00:18:10.050 align:middle line:84%
and the physiological
activity of the other.

00:18:10.050 --> 00:18:12.860 align:middle line:84%
This suggests that there is
some way in which information

00:18:12.860 --> 00:18:16.520 align:middle line:84%
is transferred that
isn't accountable

00:18:16.520 --> 00:18:19.910 align:middle line:84%
