that at least one third

00:22:12.570 --> 00:22:15.390 align:middle line:84%
of all healings, including
drugs and surgery

00:22:15.390 --> 00:22:17.910 align:middle line:84%
and other allopathic
interventions, one

00:22:17.910 --> 00:22:21.090 align:middle line:84%
